{"tid":1330126,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"IGN發表「任天堂掌機續航能力」一覽表，包括Switch Lite，3DS，GBA等所有任天堂掌機","createTime":"2019-07-18T12:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T19:01:11.000Z","uid":75050,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"260901ab54ebcb20e8ba98e16e9121467659ab6c","tid":1330126,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:20:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2382048928732281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2382048928732281&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE5sm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=e3c112c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2382048928732281</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAFpZe6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAFpZe6.jpg&h=fbebe12e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n【Nintendo】任天堂昨日（17日）晚宣布將於8月1日推出一個新的Switch機型，有著更長的續航能力。新機型是基於老版Switch而非最新公佈的Switch Lite，將電池續航能力從2.5-6.5個小時增至4.5-9個小時。<br />\n<br />\n單從續航能力上說，這算是一個很不錯的提升，但新Switch的續航能力和其他掌機對比表現又如何呢？今日IGN製作了一張圖表，非常直觀地展現了任天堂掌機在續航能力上的表現，包括Switch Lite，3DS，GBA等。<br />\n<br />\n可以看到續航最長的掌機為GameBoy和其他後續機型，都是15小時，遙遙領先新Switch的9小時。不過後者的續航能力也算是老任掌機中續航表現非常靠前的了。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，IGN還在站內文章中提到了索尼掌機PSP和PSV。<br />\n<br />\nPSP-3000電池續航為4-6個小時，相比新Switch，續航短了5-3個小時，而PSV Slim也是一樣，續航4-6個小時，比新Switch短了5-3個小時。<br />\n<br />\n-----<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9DVtGts.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9DVtGts.png&h=3edc3ae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Eh0xz7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Eh0xz7.png&h=cb1699ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f989e45f74e828d6b795bdab4ef5bc5d30b7ae55","tid":1330126,"uid":40980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:35:44.000Z","msg":"game boy 邊撚到有16個鐘呀？買貴電芯都係4-5個鐘要換電"},{"pid":"8bbcc3b287908773f07e9dd26f5729906f980541","tid":1